dc_title_s: Map of a portion of the Upper Scioto River Basin showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Scale bar left right corner of map.|Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks of the lower portion of the upper Scioto River Basin and quality of underground water.|Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.|"Prepared by JAMES J.
